Text: Request for pipeline infoIm not sure if you are the person I need to be contacting so if youre not maybe you can lead me in the right direction I am in the process of working on a gas well in Hodgeman County Kansas Section TS RW The BTU test for a well in the vicinity came back at BTU Methane Ethane Propane Isobutane Normal Butane Isopentane Normal Pentane Hexanes Mole is Methane Ethane Propane Isobutane Normal Butane Isopentane Normal Pentane Hexanes Nitrogen Oxygen Carbon Dioxide Helium and Hydrogen Do you have a pipeline in the vicinity and would you be able to purchase or transport the forementioned quality of gas If you could inform me on pipelines who could service this well please send me an email Thank you Jeff Kidd EEFSI Send and receive Hotmail on your mobile device
